            <h2>1.  Nutrition & Diet</h2>
            <div class="col1 sec1">
                <ul>
                    <li>Eat a balanced diet with plenty of fruits, vegetables, whole grains, and lean proteins.</li>
                    <li>Stay hydrated by drinking at least 2-3 liters of water daily.</li>
                    <li>Limit processed foods, sugary drinks, and excessive salt intake.</li>
                    <li>Include healthy fats like nuts, seeds, and olive oil in your meals.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col2">
                <img src="images/nutrition.jpg">
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section">
                <h2>2. Physical Activity</h2>
                <div class="col1 sec2">
                <ul>
                    <li>Aim for at least 30 minutes of moderate exercise (walking, jogging, cycling) most days of the week.</li>
                    <li>Strength training twice a week helps maintain muscle mass.</li>
                    <li>Take short breaks to stretch if you have a desk job.</li>
                </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col2">
                    <img src="images/physical_activity.jpg">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section">
                <h2>3. Mental Well-being</h2>
                <div class="col1 sec3">
                <ul>
                    <li>Get 7-9 hours of quality sleep every night.</li>
                    <li>Practice stress-relief techniques like meditation, deep breathing, or yoga.</li>
                    <li>Stay socially connected with friends and family.</li>
                    <li>Take breaks from screens and digital devices.</li>
                </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col2 img3">
                    <img src="images/mental.jpg">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section">
                <h2>4. Preventive Care</h2>
                <div class="col1 sec4">
                <ul>
                    <li>Go for regular health check-ups and screenings.</li>
                    <li>Maintain proper hygiene, including regular hand washing.</li>
                    <li>Get vaccinated and stay updated on immunizations.</li>
                </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col2 img4">
                    <img src="images/preventive.avif">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section">
                <h2>5. Lifestyle Habits</h2>
                <div class="col1 sec5">
                <ul>
                    <li>Avoid smoking, excessive alcohol, and drug use.</li>
                    <li>Maintain a healthy weight through proper diet and exercise.</li>
                    <li>Practice safe sun exposure by using sunscreen.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
                
